{"title":"Thor thunders into MTB with Aaron Gwin & the all-new 2022 Assist collection","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/09/thor-thunders-into-mtb-with-aaron-gwin-the-all-new-2022-assist-collection/","date":1628518257000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Many MTB riders have some interest in motocross too, so most of us have at least heard of Thor clothing and gear. Thor has been making motocross apparel since 1968, and they’ve finally decided to jump into the MTB world… in a big way! To launch their first ever bike line, they’ve sponsored DH racing superstar Aaron Gwin. Gwin is no stranger to moto bikes, which he raced as a teen (between his BMX and MTB years).</p><p>Thor’s new MTB gear is called the Assist Collection. Their initial release includes jerseys, shorts, pants and gloves, covering everyone’s needs from recreational trail riders to downhill racers. Fans of Intense Bikes will be stoked to see Thor is offering all the Assist pieces in Intense factory racing colors and graphics alongside their own designs.</p><h2>Thor Assist MTB Jerseys</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x557/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, React SS jersey\" width=\"695\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 695w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey-261x300.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 261w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey-104x120.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 104w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey-365x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 695px) 100vw, 695px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x557/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" ezoid=\"0.9820752135524291\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 695w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey-261x300.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 261w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey-104x120.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 104w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163554/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-React-jersey-365x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 365w\"></a></p><p>Thor’s new Assist short sleeve jerseys are made from a durable polyester fabric that wicks moisture. They offer a performance fit, and feature Thor’s hybrid set-in sleeves.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, Shiver SS jersey\" width=\"695\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey.jpg 695w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey-261x300.jpg 261w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey-104x120.jpg 104w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey-365x420.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 695px) 100vw, 695px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey.jpg 695w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey-261x300.jpg 261w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey-104x120.jpg 104w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163559/Thor-Assist-MTB-SS-Shiver-jersey-365x420.jpg 365w\"></a></p><p>The short sleeve jerseys sell for $39.95, and come in two graphics that each offer two colorways. The ‘React’ jerseys come in grey/purple or midnight/teal, while the ‘Shiver’ style comes in black/grey or teal/midnight.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163624/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-SS-jersey.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163624/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-SS-jersey.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, Intense SS jersey\" width=\"714\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0