08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, Banger LS jersey\" width=\"661\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey.jpg 661w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey-248x300.jpg 248w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey-99x120.jpg 99w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey-347x420.jpg 347w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 661px) 100vw, 661px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey.jpg 661w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey-248x300.jpg 248w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey-99x120.jpg 99w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163542/Thor-Assist-MTB-LS-Banger-jersey-347x420.jpg 347w\"></a></p><p>The new Assist long sleeve jerseys are simply a full-coverage version of the short sleeve jerseys, sharing the same polyester main fabric, set-in sleeves and performance fit. The long sleeve models cost $44.95, and come in two designs/colorways: There’s black/grey or a ‘Banger’ black/charcoal style (pictured above).</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, Intense LS jersey\" width=\"773\" height=\"506\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey.jpg 773w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-297x194.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-768x503.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-696x456.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-642x420.jpg 642w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-741x486.jpg 741w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 773px) 100vw, 773px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey.jpg 773w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-297x194.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-768x503.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-696x456.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-642x420.jpg 642w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163609/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-LS-jersey-741x486.jpg 741w\"></a></p><p>The Intense Long Sleeve jersey comes in one black/charcoal Team colorway only, and retails for $49.95. All of Thor’s jerseys are available in sizes XS-2XL.</p><h3>Assist MTB Shorts/Pants</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, shorts\" width=\"665\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short.jpg 665w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short-249x300.jpg 249w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short-100x120.jpg 100w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short-349x420.jpg 349w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 665px) 100vw, 665px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short.jpg 665w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short-249x300.jpg 249w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short-100x120.jpg 100w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163548/Thor-Assist-MTB-short-349x420.jpg 349w\"></a></strong>Thor brought their extensive experience to their new moto-inspired Assist MTB short. The shorts are made from In-Motion fabric, and include a rear yoke stretch panel for a solid fit in riding position. The waistline boasts silicone printing and side cinches for adjustment, and the fly uses both a hook and loop closure and a single button. The shorts offer two zippered pockets for storage, and laser-cut crotch ventilation. The Assist MTB short sells for $79.95, and comes in black or teal colors.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, Intense shorts\" width=\"616\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short.jpg 616w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short-231x300.jpg 231w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short-92x120.jpg 92w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short-323x420.jpg 323w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 616px) 100vw, 616px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short.jpg 616w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short-231x300.jpg 231w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short-92x120.jpg 92w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163619/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-short-323x420.jpg 323w\"></a></p><p>The Intense MTB short is functionally the same as the MTB short. They retail for $89.95, and come in black or grey.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, Intense pants\" width=\"700\" height=\"502\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants.jpg 700w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants-297x213.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants-120x86.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants-696x499.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants-586x420.jpg 586w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants.jpg 700w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants-297x213.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants-120x86.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants-696x499.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163614/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-pants-586x420.jpg 586w\"></a></p><p>If you want Thor pants, I hope you like Intense Racing because they are only offering the pants with Intense graphics (Gwin needs a full kit for the races!). Like the shorts, the Intense Assist MTB pants are made from In-Motion fabric, and have a rear yoke stretch panel. They also include laser-cut ventilation and mesh panels in key areas to keep you cool. The waist uses a ratchet-style closure, has silicone printing inside, and cinches at the sides for a precise fit. Two zippered pockets carry your trail/bike park essentials. &nbsp;MSRP for the Intense Assist MTB Pant is $109.95.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, liner short\" width=\"664\" height=\"439\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short.jpg 664w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short-297x196.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short-635x420.jpg 635w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 664px) 100vw, 664px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short.jpg 664w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short-297x196.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163538/Thor-Assist-MTB-liner-short-635x420.jpg 635w\"></a></p><p>The Assist Liner Short provides some saddle padding with a multi-density TMF Moete 3 chamois. The liners feature a 1.5” elastic waistband and an 8” inseam length. &nbsp;A compression fit and silicone printing on the lower legs ensure a snug fit, and low-profile flatlock stitching should keep the seams from rubbing you the wrong way. The liner short sells for $39.95, and comes in black only.</p><p>All pants, shorts and liner shorts are available in waist sizes 28-40.</p><h3>Assist MTB Gloves</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, gloves\" width=\"800\" height=\"462\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove-297x172.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove-120x69.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove-768x444.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove-696x402.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove-727x420.jpg 727w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove-297x172.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove-120x69.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove-768x444.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove-696x402.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163533/Thor-Assist-MTB-glove-727x420.jpg 727w\"></a></strong>Finally, to complete your kit you need matching gloves! The Assist glove follows a minimalist design, but includes a few key features; the fingertips have silicone printed graphics for solid brake lever control, and the palms are made from perforated Clarino. The wrist offers a low-profile hook and loop closure on the underside, and the inner thumb is wrapped for durability. Thor’s Assist Glove sells for $24.95, and your color options are black/grey, midnight/teal or grey/purple.</p><figure id=\"attachment_267575\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-267575\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove.jpg\" alt=\"Thor Assist MTB, Intense gloves\" width=\"800\" height=\"462\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove-297x172.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove-120x69.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove-768x444.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove-696x402.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove-727x420.jpg 727w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove-297x172.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove-120x69.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove-768x444.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove-696x402.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/08163604/Thor-Intense-Assist-MTB-glove-727x420.jpg 727w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-267575\">*Images c. Thor</figcaption></figure><p>Last up, the Intense Assist Glove is the same as the above model except for the graphics. The Intense style sells for $27.95, and they come in ‘Dart’ black/red, ‘Team’ black/red, or ‘Chex’ black/grey. Thor’s MTB gloves are available in sizes XS-2XL.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.thormx.com/bike/\"><em>thormx.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"S